         "a": "Nasal washings/nasopharyngeal swabs, blood culture, sputum culture, pleural fluid culture, bronchoscopic fluid/BAL washings, lung aspirate studies, serology, nucleic acid amplification test, and countercurrent immuno-electrophoresis of urine."
