         "q": "Outline the prevention of pneumonia.",
         "a": "Immunization against respiratory pathogens (measles, diphtheria, pertussis, H. influenzae); health education (reduce overcrowding, adequate nutrition, breastfeeding, avoid kissing children when having an RTI, reduce cigarette and wood smoke); and legislation to reduce environmental pollution and discourage smoking."
